{"tid":1835901,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[置頂]警世!香港人若再不行動香港將會數日內淪陷!","createTime":"2020-01-23T04:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T05:04:49.000Z","uid":287028,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"02bec7a6cbf7d16987c13d49bdd6acfd7c7845b2","tid":1835901,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eO3VjJF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeO3VjJF.jpg&h=560a34db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#24Jan #高鐵 #肺炎 #自發<br />\n<br />\n緊急呼籲！請廣傳！<br />\n有監於武漢肺炎病例數量急遽上升現在在此呼籲明天24/1 12:30 於西九龍高鐵站周邊舉行緊急集會以防止疫情擴散至香港各個地區。請大家幫忙分享並在公海多加討論以提高傳閱率，大家必定，務必小心並帶上口罩以防中蕉。<br />\n有免疫系統疾病嘅人唔可以去<br />\n<br />\n高鐵西九站圍封行動<br />\n日期 : 1月24日 （五）<br />\n時間 : 12:30<br />\n地點 : 港鐵柯士甸站<br />\n           油麻地站<br />\n           尖沙咀站<br />\n*參與者必須做好個人防疫措施<br />\n*老弱婦孺不建議前往<br />\n*有免疫系統疾病患者不能前往<br />\n*帶備飲管方便補充水分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/suckhighspeed0123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsuckhighspeed0123&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=c73f6708\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/suckhighspeed0123</a>"},{"pid":"4834f14c1c6a1c33c5ab44c881e556df9a13b74f","tid":1835901,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:25:04.000Z","msg":"求大家推行動post救香港，<br />\n好人一生平安"},{"pid":"8e40a333a1a8924e0a6e9cc030be75f2e0e20541","tid":1835901,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:25:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ea1524df856326d3ceb5d52124b547ce65bb6b6","tid":1835901,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:30:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29e749f022b1d4a077b1f1059dbcc2ce13c3323f","tid":1835901,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:41:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"485452598c0e8590430d1a72d0fb91b460e94728","tid":1835901,"uid":252187,"like":0,